daaayyyyyyuuummnnnn!!!&nbsp;

forgot all about this motha-trucka! i was actually thinking of checking this thing out a&nbsp;few days ago but good ol' johnny homesleep left me a grand comment that sent my heart racing, so i just HAD to log in and see what the world of LJ had become.

Not much has happened since i last posted in here.&nbsp;broke up with nicole, had sexy ass sex with a few girls, moved... um. band stuff. i don't know. good things and bad things but the new year is here and 2008 is gonna be GREAT!

that's my motto for the year.

ok, live has gotten more adult and boring&nbsp;but i'm still striving to hang on to the way i felt in college. the good years when i didn't have to work and all i did was make music haha. alright, i'm outtie!&nbsp;
